    <item>
      <title>铃木将停止在泰国生产汽车，转而专注于电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/suzuki-to-stop-making-cars-in-thailand-to-focus-on-ev-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铃木汽车公司周五表示，该公司将于明年年底停止在泰国的轿车和卡车生产，以集中资源在其他地方生产电动和混合动力汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/suzuki-to-stop-making-cars-in-thailand-to-focus-on-ev-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:35:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
